These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, soul
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of soul is not to the right of the fan of soul##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | soul | punk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, scientific
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person watching scientific movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | spy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, fish
1. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
2. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
3. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | goat | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, boat
1. the person driving the tram is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | tram | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-5::.
